WEBVTT

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:53.120
Honey.

00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:58.830
Are you sure we're moving to Bali?

00:01:00.450 --> 00:01:03.910
Are you quitting your job in Jakarta?

00:01:04.910 --> 00:01:07.200
It's not like I'm leaving my job forever.

00:01:07.290 --> 00:01:09.500
Dad can take care of the company.

00:01:11.450 --> 00:01:13.000
We don't have children yet.

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:14.830
The doctor said

00:01:14.910 --> 00:01:16.660
if we need to reset,

00:01:16.750 --> 00:01:19.450
we have to travel and relax.

00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:21.250
You want to have children, right?

00:01:25.950 --> 00:01:27.410
I really do, honey.

00:01:28.370 --> 00:01:32.120
We've been married for five years.

00:01:32.830 --> 00:01:34.950
We haven't had children until now.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.330
If this is what's best for us,

00:01:41.450 --> 00:01:43.580
I'll follow what you say.

00:01:48.290 --> 00:01:51.080
All right then. Tomorrow,
we'll leave for Bali.

00:02:43.370 --> 00:02:46.450
Sorry, five years ago at your wedding,

00:02:46.540 --> 00:02:47.620
I couldn't come

00:02:47.700 --> 00:02:50.660
because my mom was sick at the same time.

00:02:51.620 --> 00:02:53.580
Yeah, that's okay, Den.

00:02:53.660 --> 00:02:56.250
Besides, you already
gave me a lot of souvenirs.

00:02:56.330 --> 00:02:57.846
That's more than enough. Right, honey?

00:02:57.870 --> 00:02:59.660
- Yes. - Thank you, okay?

00:02:59.750 --> 00:03:02.056
Thanks to you. You're always
there whenever we come to Bali.

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:05.000
If I go to Jakarta, you're
the one who picks me up.

00:03:06.660 --> 00:03:10.750
Right, what if you stay
with us at our villa?

00:03:10.830 --> 00:03:12.790
Right, there are three rooms.

00:03:12.870 --> 00:03:14.410
One for me and Sandra,

00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:16.790
one for the villa's
guard, and one more for you.

00:03:16.870 --> 00:03:17.910
Yeah, come on.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.620
I can't spend the night there.

00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:21.136
But if I visit you occasionally
and don't spend the night,

00:03:21.160 --> 00:03:22.750
that can be arranged.

00:03:22.830 --> 00:03:25.830
Promise me you'll visit
me. Don't break your promise.

00:03:25.910 --> 00:03:27.790
Yes, San.

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:30.500
I'll drop by if I don't
have any makeup jobs.

00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:31.580
Make up?

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:35.700
Hey, we've arrived in
Ubud. Where is your villa?

00:03:35.790 --> 00:03:37.290
Where exactly is the villa?

00:03:37.370 --> 00:03:39.410
I don't know the exact address too.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:42.120
Did you just buy a villa
without surveying it first?

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.160
It was my friend's villa.

00:03:44.250 --> 00:03:45.596
I haven't had time to survey it yet.

00:03:45.620 --> 00:03:47.160
I'd like to see it too.

00:03:47.250 --> 00:03:48.160
What is the name of the villa?

00:03:48.250 --> 00:03:49.580
Alam Sembuwuk Villa.

00:03:51.250 --> 00:03:54.200
Never mind. Look it up on the
map. Let's not keep going in circles.

00:04:00.250 --> 00:04:02.580
Good afternoon.

00:04:04.250 --> 00:04:05.330
Good afternoon.

00:04:05.410 --> 00:04:07.000
Good afternoon, sir.

00:04:07.620 --> 00:04:10.790
Were you ordered by Mr. Agung
to look after this villa?

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:11.870
Yes, sir.

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.580
Just call me Mr. Rai.

00:04:14.660 --> 00:04:16.660
- Please come in. - Thank you, Mr. Rai.

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:18.790
- Let me bring the suitcase, okay? - Okay.

00:04:19.870 --> 00:04:22.660
The villa's atmosphere is
nice. It feels so natural.

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:24.330
Away from noise.

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:29.000
Okay then, you married couple.

00:04:29.080 --> 00:04:32.040
I can't accompany you for now
because I have a makeup job.

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:34.500
So I'll go back first.
I'll come back tomorrow.

00:04:34.580 --> 00:04:37.870
- Okay? - But do come here tomorrow, okay?

00:04:37.950 --> 00:04:41.830
Deal! Consider it done.

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:42.790
All right then.

00:04:42.870 --> 00:04:44.830
- Be careful and thank you. - Bye.

00:05:23.540 --> 00:05:25.750
I feel

00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:27.330
an aura of awakening.

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:33.410
It's like there is Leyak
magic starting to emerge.

00:05:35.290 --> 00:05:37.410
I hope everything turns out fine.

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.370
The switch is here, ma'am.

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:43.540
It's you, Mr. Rai. I
wonder who it was earlier.

00:06:43.620 --> 00:06:44.620
Thank you.

00:06:45.660 --> 00:06:46.660
Sir.

00:07:16.870 --> 00:07:19.370
Yes, come on. Hurry up.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:24.200
Hello. All right.

00:07:25.200 --> 00:07:26.120
Thank you.

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:30.120
Now we've arrived at my
uncle's water sports place.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:33.500
You have to try all the rides here.

00:07:33.580 --> 00:07:35.370
Are you ready?

00:07:35.450 --> 00:07:37.000
- Ready! - Ready!

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:38.886
But San, aren't you worried
your skin will get darker?

00:07:38.910 --> 00:07:41.200
Sorry, but if I am with my husband,

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:42.620
I'm not afraid of that.

00:07:42.700 --> 00:07:44.250
Yeah, never mind! Let's go in!

00:07:47.660 --> 00:07:49.160
Look!

00:07:49.250 --> 00:07:53.620
Look at the stretch of
beach before our eyes.

00:07:53.700 --> 00:07:57.410
This holiday of yours
will be truly memorable.

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:58.950
You won't regret it.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:02.160
It's true. The beaches in
Bali are really beautiful.

00:08:02.250 --> 00:08:04.726
No matter how many times I've
come here, I never get bored of it.

00:08:04.750 --> 00:08:07.700
Yes, that's very true.
Bali is heaven on earth.

00:08:07.790 --> 00:08:11.450
Okay, if that's the case, you
guys should change clothes now.

00:08:11.540 --> 00:08:14.330
Men should change in the men's
room and women in the ladies' room.

00:08:14.410 --> 00:08:15.570
Don't simply change anywhere.

00:08:16.370 --> 00:08:18.660
- We're husband and wife though.
- Don't rush.

00:08:18.750 --> 00:08:20.750
- It's the same. - Hey.

00:08:21.290 --> 00:08:23.290
Iced tea for three, please. Okay?

00:08:24.750 --> 00:08:28.910
Enjoy this heat, dear.

00:08:31.200 --> 00:08:33.540
- Let's go, honey. - Bye.

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:25.290
Gosh, so tired.

00:09:25.370 --> 00:09:29.290
I'm sunburned. My skin is already dark.

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:31.950
And now it's getting darker.

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:33.040
Also chubbier.

00:09:33.910 --> 00:09:36.080
How was it? It was fun, right?

00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:39.330
I'd never recommend something
that isn't fun for you.

00:09:39.410 --> 00:09:40.580
Yes, it is fun.

00:09:40.660 --> 00:09:43.330
Plus, we had time to do parasailing.

00:09:43.410 --> 00:09:46.500
We could see the beauty of the
Island of the Gods from above.

00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:48.950
- It was nice. - Really cool. Den.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.540
Go and take a shower.

00:09:51.620 --> 00:09:55.160
Stay here tonight and keep me company.

00:09:55.250 --> 00:09:58.700
Later, we'll share mystical stories.

00:09:58.790 --> 00:10:00.830
Why did I even agree to stay here?

00:10:01.580 --> 00:10:02.580
Fine then.

00:10:02.620 --> 00:10:05.200
You're mistaken if you want
to ask me about mystical things,

00:10:05.290 --> 00:10:08.410
but my relative has a sixth sense.

00:10:08.500 --> 00:10:12.290
- Seriously? - That's enough.

00:10:12.370 --> 00:10:15.000
I don't believe in mystical things.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.080
Okay then.

00:10:16.160 --> 00:10:17.516
Why can't we share mystical stories?

00:10:17.540 --> 00:10:20.370
We'd better go back to our room, okay?

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.000
Here you go.

00:10:22.910 --> 00:10:25.370
Help me learn how to
use the sewing machine.

00:10:26.250 --> 00:10:27.870
Sure.

00:10:27.950 --> 00:10:30.290
Later when you are older,

00:10:30.370 --> 00:10:32.410
you can help your in-laws.

00:10:33.410 --> 00:10:34.450
All right.

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:36.200
Mom.

00:10:37.500 --> 00:10:41.450
Why did I suddenly dream of Grandma?

00:10:42.410 --> 00:10:44.040
That's normal.

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:46.410
It means you miss her.

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:50.700
No, Mom. This one is different.

00:10:51.540 --> 00:10:52.540
In my dream,

00:10:52.580 --> 00:10:55.700
she suddenly came back to life.

00:10:57.250 --> 00:10:58.790
You're so weird.

00:10:58.870 --> 00:11:01.370
How could a dead person come back to life?

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:05.500
That's why you should remember my advice.

00:11:05.580 --> 00:11:08.120
Before going to sleep, remember to pray

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:10.910
so that you don't have strange dreams.

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:12.790
That's enough.

00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:41.750
Honey.

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:45.540
Honey, you startled me!

00:11:45.620 --> 00:11:48.410
What are you doing? I've
been seeing you daydreaming.

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:51.910
- Nothing. - I know you.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.950
You must be thinking
about something, right?

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:56.250
No, honey. I don't know why.

00:11:58.040 --> 00:11:59.790
Nevermind.

00:12:00.330 --> 00:12:01.910
Let's just have a baby in Bali.

00:12:21.370 --> 00:12:22.620
It's raining outside.

00:12:24.700 --> 00:12:25.750
Why do I feel that

00:12:27.700 --> 00:12:28.910
someone is watching me?

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:31.160
San.

00:12:31.910 --> 00:12:32.910
Put.

00:12:36.370 --> 00:12:39.540
Do you really want to live in Bali?

00:12:40.620 --> 00:12:43.830
Yes, because the doctor
suggested I go on bed rest

00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:45.790
if I want to focus on having children.

00:12:46.830 --> 00:12:47.870
Moreover,

00:12:48.910 --> 00:12:50.330
I've been married for five years,

00:12:50.910 --> 00:12:52.700
but I don't have children yet.

00:12:52.790 --> 00:12:55.000
That's good, monkey.

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:58.000
Now I have a friend in Bali.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:13:00.250
- What did you call me? - No!

00:13:00.330 --> 00:13:02.790
Hey, don't call me monkey, okay?

00:13:02.870 --> 00:13:06.040
Because the monkeys on my campus
eat bananas and destroy property.

00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:07.500
Bear that in mind.

00:13:07.580 --> 00:13:08.700
What did you say earlier?

00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:10.000
To keep me company?

00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:13.080
You mean someone will
accompany you to watch movies,

00:13:13.160 --> 00:13:16.450
pay for food, and hang out, right?

00:13:16.540 --> 00:13:18.410
I don't have enough money.

00:13:18.500 --> 00:13:21.410
Killing two birds with one stone.

00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:23.580
Do my nails look nice?

00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:25.620
They're nice.

00:13:25.700 --> 00:13:27.620
Please do my nails too.

00:13:27.700 --> 00:13:30.500
These hairy feet look
like moss growing on them.

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:50.080
What are you doing here?

00:13:56.330 --> 00:13:57.370
What are you doing, San?

00:13:57.450 --> 00:13:59.250
Spying on people preparing offerings.

00:14:00.660 --> 00:14:02.450
Den, I want to ask you.

00:14:02.540 --> 00:14:05.870
Why do I always see him giving
the offerings every night?

00:14:06.790 --> 00:14:09.750
What could it mean? Does
he practice black magic?

00:14:10.370 --> 00:14:13.120
At this day and age, why do
you still believe in those things?

00:14:13.200 --> 00:14:14.450
Hush, don't simply say things.

00:14:14.540 --> 00:14:17.120
He's not practicing black magic.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:19.620
In fact, every Hindu community in Bali

00:14:19.700 --> 00:14:22.000
performs offerings as a tradition

00:14:22.830 --> 00:14:25.370
for the seen and the unseen, for God,

00:14:25.450 --> 00:14:27.370
and for invisible beings.

00:14:27.910 --> 00:14:29.540
Take a look at this villa.

00:14:30.870 --> 00:14:32.150
It's far from the crowds, right?

00:14:33.540 --> 00:14:34.540
That makes it vulnerable

00:14:35.160 --> 00:14:36.830
to unseen beings.

00:14:37.450 --> 00:14:40.870
Local people call them wong samar.

00:14:43.700 --> 00:14:46.830
Right, do you remember when you
picked me up in Bali back then?

00:14:48.370 --> 00:14:50.700
You took me to the villa
that my friend recommended.

00:14:51.790 --> 00:14:55.120
That villa had a strong
mystical aura. Do you remember?

00:14:55.200 --> 00:14:56.290
Yes, I remember.

00:14:56.370 --> 00:14:58.410
That's why I didn't take you inside, right?

00:14:58.500 --> 00:15:01.580
Enough, it's better if we
don't discuss things like this.

00:15:04.330 --> 00:15:05.790
See?

00:15:05.870 --> 00:15:07.080
Believe it or not,

00:15:07.620 --> 00:15:09.870
the mystical things in Bali
are very strong, you know?

00:15:10.410 --> 00:15:12.910
This is just a power outage,
not due to anything mystical.

00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:16.620
Mr. Rai, turn on the lights.

00:15:18.410 --> 00:15:19.660
The lights are back.

00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:22.700
This has nothing to do
with supernatural beings.

00:15:23.330 --> 00:15:24.870
See? It's off again.

00:15:25.620 --> 00:15:27.250
We're being pranked, you know?

00:15:27.330 --> 00:15:29.130
Putra, it's better if
you say you believe it.

00:15:31.450 --> 00:15:32.870
I'm scared.

00:15:32.950 --> 00:15:34.350
I'm sleeping with you guys tonight.

00:15:34.410 --> 00:15:37.160
You're a guy. Why bother
us on our honeymoon?

00:15:37.250 --> 00:15:38.870
Honey, what are you doing?

00:15:38.950 --> 00:15:40.426
It's already bad enough
that he sleeps alone.

00:15:40.450 --> 00:15:42.700
Yes, you're really heartless, aren't you?

00:15:42.790 --> 00:15:44.500
I'm going to my room.

00:15:45.160 --> 00:15:46.330
This villa is really scary.

00:15:59.950 --> 00:16:01.080
Luh.

00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:03.410
I've finished everything.

00:16:03.500 --> 00:16:04.910
Now let's pray

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:07.500
so that your grandma's
spirit will rest in peace.

00:16:07.580 --> 00:16:08.580
Okay.

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:57.750
Since the people from Jakarta came here,

00:16:59.370 --> 00:17:01.910
strange things have been
happening at this villa.

00:17:04.910 --> 00:17:07.410
Maybe they learned black magic.

00:18:14.040 --> 00:18:15.040
Honey.

00:18:16.080 --> 00:18:17.830
Honey, what's wrong with you?

00:18:17.910 --> 00:18:19.160
You're okay, right?

00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:24.120
I just had a bad dream.

00:18:26.450 --> 00:18:29.830
This must be because of what Denny said.

00:18:31.370 --> 00:18:33.410
I told you not to think about it.

00:18:33.500 --> 00:18:34.950
Don't dwell on strange things.

00:18:36.200 --> 00:18:39.000
I bring you here to Bali so we can be happy

00:18:39.080 --> 00:18:40.450
and we can have a reset.

00:18:41.330 --> 00:18:43.450
Not talk about mystical things with Denny.

00:18:44.080 --> 00:18:46.200
Yes, honey. I'm sorry.

00:18:48.790 --> 00:18:49.790
Okay then.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:53.290
Now let's just sleep.

00:18:58.200 --> 00:18:59.080
Good morning!

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:02.120
Rise and shine! Time to wake up!

00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:05.540
Don't just focus on making
a baby. Wake up early.

00:19:05.620 --> 00:19:08.160
Putra, you don't want to
miss your flight, right?

00:19:08.250 --> 00:19:10.500
Wake up, dear.

00:19:12.620 --> 00:19:13.910
He's so noisy.

00:19:15.870 --> 00:19:17.620
Wake up, honey. It's already afternoon.

00:19:23.750 --> 00:19:27.660
Gosh, honey. It's already 11
a.m. My flight is at two, right?

00:19:27.750 --> 00:19:29.290
Hurry up and take a shower, honey.

00:19:29.370 --> 00:19:30.636
I'm afraid there'll be heavy traffic.

00:19:30.660 --> 00:19:32.120
Yes, I'll get ready first.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.000
- I'll wait outside, honey. - Okay.

00:19:36.910 --> 00:19:39.870
So noisy. People are sleeping.

00:19:40.700 --> 00:19:43.200
Your face…

00:19:44.410 --> 00:19:46.910
It was good, wasn't it?

00:19:49.500 --> 00:19:52.660
How was it? Was it good?

00:19:54.250 --> 00:19:55.330
Did you stay up late?

00:19:56.040 --> 00:19:57.410
How many times?

00:19:57.500 --> 00:20:00.016
If I didn't wake you up, no way
you would be awake at this hour.

00:20:00.040 --> 00:20:01.450
What do you mean staying up?

00:20:01.540 --> 00:20:03.040
I had a nightmare last night.

00:20:04.830 --> 00:20:07.450
What kind of nightmare
when you're enjoying it?

00:20:09.290 --> 00:20:10.290
Den…

00:20:10.910 --> 00:20:13.910
I dreamed I was chased by
an old woman. It was scary.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:16.700
Oh dear. It's just an
old woman in your dream.

00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:18.476
Maybe she wanted to
hang out. Right, Mr. Rai?

00:20:18.500 --> 00:20:20.620
Would you like me to make you coffee?

00:20:20.700 --> 00:20:22.250
Could you make two, please?

00:20:22.330 --> 00:20:24.830
- Okay. - What did you just say?

00:20:25.540 --> 00:20:26.726
Hanging out with an old woman?

00:20:26.750 --> 00:20:28.660
So do you mean I really want

00:20:28.750 --> 00:20:30.386
- to be chased by an old woman?
- Calm down.

00:20:30.410 --> 00:20:32.290
Calm down. Don't stress.

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:33.620
Eat first. It's still early.

00:20:33.700 --> 00:20:34.750
I was just kidding.

00:20:34.830 --> 00:20:37.370
Eat up, it's delicious.

00:20:40.040 --> 00:20:41.480
Come on, let's hurry to the airport.

00:20:41.540 --> 00:20:43.660
Wait a second. I haven't worn my shoes yet.

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:46.580
Honey, I made you tea. Drink first.

00:20:46.660 --> 00:20:48.000
Thanks.

00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:51.540
Honey, I'm going to the airport first.

00:20:51.620 --> 00:20:52.790
Take care of yourself, okay?

00:20:52.870 --> 00:20:53.950
Don't think too much.

00:20:54.040 --> 00:20:56.200
How long will you be in Jakarta?

00:20:56.290 --> 00:20:58.290
Once all my work is finished,

00:20:58.370 --> 00:21:00.700
I can leave it to Dad and
come back here right away.

00:21:00.790 --> 00:21:02.120
Don't take too long, okay?

00:21:02.200 --> 00:21:04.410
- Okay. - Come on, I'm ready.

00:21:04.500 --> 00:21:06.250
- Come on, hurry. - Bye.

00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:08.580
Honey. Hey, San, hurry up.

00:21:08.660 --> 00:21:10.160
I can't stay tonight.

00:21:10.250 --> 00:21:12.500
Then I will be alone here?

00:21:12.580 --> 00:21:15.060
Putra is going to Jakarta and
you aren't staying here tonight.

00:21:15.290 --> 00:21:17.290
You are so spoiled.

00:21:17.870 --> 00:21:19.080
Calm down.

00:21:19.160 --> 00:21:21.700
I'll send my relative to accompany you.

00:21:22.540 --> 00:21:24.830
The one who is a great singer.

00:21:24.910 --> 00:21:26.660
- Let's hurry! - Let's go.

00:21:29.700 --> 00:21:33.540
Greetings.

00:21:34.910 --> 00:21:36.040
So, Jero.

00:21:36.700 --> 00:21:39.870
Many people say I can
see supernatural beings

00:21:39.950 --> 00:21:43.370
even though I've never learned Leyak magic,

00:21:44.370 --> 00:21:45.620
Wait a second.

00:21:59.080 --> 00:22:00.250
Sorry, child.

00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:03.580
At this moment,

00:22:04.250 --> 00:22:07.330
you truly can do Leyak magic.

00:22:08.410 --> 00:22:12.290
It was passed down to you.

00:22:14.500 --> 00:22:16.870
Recently, did someone

00:22:17.580 --> 00:22:20.200
in your family die

00:22:20.870 --> 00:22:23.830
and ask you to be near them

00:22:23.910 --> 00:22:25.120
at the time of their death?

00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:28.290
Yes, it was my grandma.

00:22:28.830 --> 00:22:32.410
I also dreamed of being
with my grandma at the grave.

00:22:32.500 --> 00:22:35.330
The dream means

00:22:35.410 --> 00:22:38.370
that her knowledge of Leyak magic

00:22:38.450 --> 00:22:40.500
was passed down to you.

00:22:40.580 --> 00:22:44.500
So how do I get rid of this?

00:22:45.870 --> 00:22:49.450
You can return the knowledge of Leyak magic

00:22:49.540 --> 00:22:51.040
at Pura Dalem

00:22:51.120 --> 00:22:53.000
or Pura Prajapati.

00:22:53.750 --> 00:22:55.830
At exactly midnight

00:22:55.910 --> 00:22:58.120
on Friday Kliwon night.

00:22:58.200 --> 00:23:00.500
But I am so scared.

00:23:01.080 --> 00:23:02.450
Don't worry.

00:23:03.080 --> 00:23:06.290
I'll help and look after you, child.

00:23:07.040 --> 00:23:09.000
If that's the case, thank you.

00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:13.500
Ma'am.

00:23:14.080 --> 00:23:15.080
Someone's here for you.

00:23:15.160 --> 00:23:16.160
Yes.

00:23:19.410 --> 00:23:21.290
Are you Gayatri, Denny's relative?

00:23:21.370 --> 00:23:22.540
Yes, I'm Gayatri.

00:23:22.620 --> 00:23:23.910
I'm Sandra.

00:23:25.330 --> 00:23:28.200
You didn't bring a bag?
Didn't you plan on staying here?

00:23:28.290 --> 00:23:29.540
It's in my car.

00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:30.540
I see.

00:23:30.620 --> 00:23:33.540
Could you take Gayatri's
bag and bring it here?

00:23:33.620 --> 00:23:35.200
- Okay, ma'am. - Thanks.

00:23:35.290 --> 00:23:37.330
- Let's chat inside. - Come on.

00:23:38.040 --> 00:23:39.790
How was it? Is it hard to find this place?

00:23:39.870 --> 00:23:41.160
It's not that hard.

00:23:45.160 --> 00:23:46.160
Right, Gayatri.

00:23:46.830 --> 00:23:48.870
Do you really have a sixth sense?

00:23:49.620 --> 00:23:50.950
Yes, I do.

00:23:51.040 --> 00:23:53.330
Balinese people call it melik.

00:23:55.200 --> 00:23:56.500
Right.

00:23:56.580 --> 00:23:57.910
Can I ask something?

00:23:58.950 --> 00:24:01.200
Sure. What do you want to know?

00:24:01.290 --> 00:24:02.620
Why are you so serious?

00:24:03.370 --> 00:24:04.370
Do you

00:24:05.870 --> 00:24:07.450
learn Leyak magic?

00:24:08.160 --> 00:24:09.830
Leyak magic?

00:24:09.910 --> 00:24:12.500
Of course not. You're kidding, aren't you?

00:24:12.580 --> 00:24:15.250
I can't possibly learn that.

00:24:16.790 --> 00:24:18.370
Why did you ask?

00:24:18.450 --> 00:24:21.410
No, I'm just asking.

00:24:22.790 --> 00:24:26.370
I often heard stories about Leyak magic,

00:24:26.450 --> 00:24:29.000
but I don't know until now

00:24:29.080 --> 00:24:31.160
what Leyak magic looks like.

00:24:31.250 --> 00:24:35.080
Actually, Leyak magic is
meant for self-protection,

00:24:35.160 --> 00:24:37.450
but because human nature is greedy,

00:24:37.540 --> 00:24:39.700
it's usually misused.

00:24:40.330 --> 00:24:43.080
Yes, it depends on the person.

00:24:50.870 --> 00:24:51.870
Keep going.

00:24:55.370 --> 00:24:58.080
Gosh, my dearly beloved child.

00:24:58.160 --> 00:24:59.450
Drink some milk first, okay?

00:25:07.910 --> 00:25:09.000
Stop that nonsense.

00:25:09.080 --> 00:25:11.330
Hurry and finish the milk.

00:25:20.790 --> 00:25:23.660
Don't be fussy. Just finish your drink.

00:25:23.750 --> 00:25:26.080
I'm going to sleep. My darling is waiting.

00:25:27.950 --> 00:25:29.330
- I love you. - Finish it.

00:27:19.040 --> 00:27:20.910
It turns out I forgot to close the window.

00:27:28.500 --> 00:27:31.330
Oh my, you keep looking
younger and younger.

00:27:31.410 --> 00:27:34.250
She dresses up all the
time. Isn't that right, Rik?

00:27:34.330 --> 00:27:38.370
Hey, if I look young, you'll be proud too.

00:27:39.120 --> 00:27:41.580
If you look young, I feel happy too.

00:27:41.660 --> 00:27:42.910
Oh dear.

00:27:44.080 --> 00:27:46.950
This one puts on makeup every day.

00:27:48.620 --> 00:27:51.040
Children are prohibited
from making comments.

00:28:44.750 --> 00:28:45.910
Where is Sandra?

00:29:13.870 --> 00:29:15.200
Hey.

00:29:15.750 --> 00:29:17.450
What's wrong, Gayatri?

00:29:18.080 --> 00:29:20.500
Why are you running
until you're out of breath?

00:29:20.580 --> 00:29:21.580
What's wrong?

00:29:22.700 --> 00:29:24.750
Was that not you earlier?

00:29:27.620 --> 00:29:28.620
No.

00:29:31.040 --> 00:29:33.450
Have a drink first.

00:29:38.910 --> 00:29:40.120
Why?

00:29:41.700 --> 00:29:42.700
Nothing.

00:29:45.410 --> 00:29:47.830
Okay then. Calm down, okay?

00:29:47.910 --> 00:29:49.830
Just sleep in my room.

00:29:49.910 --> 00:29:51.200
I can sleep alone.

00:29:52.370 --> 00:29:53.660
It's all right.

00:29:53.750 --> 00:29:54.790
Calm down.

00:29:56.330 --> 00:29:58.200
OPEN

00:30:02.910 --> 00:30:05.660
- Hi! - Hi!

00:30:05.750 --> 00:30:08.330
Hello, Den. Welcome to Jim's Salon.

00:30:08.410 --> 00:30:09.620
Hello, miss.

00:30:09.700 --> 00:30:14.080
Today, me and this girl who is super fussy

00:30:14.160 --> 00:30:17.410
want to do treatment here.

00:30:17.500 --> 00:30:19.620
You always call me fussy

00:30:19.700 --> 00:30:21.660
even though you're the
one who is fussy, right?

00:30:21.750 --> 00:30:23.290
But you are fussy.

00:30:23.370 --> 00:30:25.790
Mainly, for her…

00:30:40.120 --> 00:30:41.700
I'm exhausted.

00:30:41.790 --> 00:30:43.120
Yeah.

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:45.040
Fortunately, it's not
raining, so we can swim.

00:30:45.790 --> 00:30:46.790
Yeah.

00:30:50.540 --> 00:30:51.620
What necklace is that, San?

00:30:52.250 --> 00:30:53.700
What necklace is that?

00:30:54.330 --> 00:30:55.410
Oh, this.

00:30:57.750 --> 00:31:00.080
Just a normal necklace, it's nothing.

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:01.160
Let's swim.

00:31:16.500 --> 00:31:18.040
Gayatri, what are you doing?

00:31:18.120 --> 00:31:20.080
You're pulling my leg again.

00:31:20.160 --> 00:31:22.080
What if I drown?

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:23.540
It's not funny.

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:32.410
How's your work in Jakarta, honey?

00:31:33.160 --> 00:31:34.700
Everything's fine.

00:31:34.790 --> 00:31:36.200
What about you?

00:31:37.160 --> 00:31:38.830
I'm fine too.

00:31:40.700 --> 00:31:43.500
Denny's relative is
here. Her name is Gayatri.

00:31:43.580 --> 00:31:47.660
Well, starting last night, she's
been staying at our villa, honey.

00:31:49.410 --> 00:31:51.450
Ever since she stayed here,

00:31:52.200 --> 00:31:54.620
many strange things have been happening.

00:31:55.950 --> 00:31:57.200
Maybe…

00:31:57.870 --> 00:31:59.790
she has a sixth sense.

00:31:59.870 --> 00:32:01.700
That's nonsense.

00:32:02.410 --> 00:32:05.660
Just because someone acts strange
doesn't mean they have a sixth sense.

00:32:06.330 --> 00:32:09.660
Yes, I don't mean it like that, but…

00:32:09.750 --> 00:32:11.080
Enough.

00:32:11.160 --> 00:32:13.870
It's better not to discuss
mystical things like this anymore.

00:32:14.500 --> 00:32:16.250
You'll just add more stress.

00:32:16.330 --> 00:32:18.290
You'd better go for a
walk with Denny instead.

00:32:19.000 --> 00:32:20.160
All right.

00:32:21.160 --> 00:32:23.160
When are you coming back here?

00:32:24.620 --> 00:32:27.580
Be patient, I'll be back soon.

00:32:28.500 --> 00:32:30.250
Okay then.

00:32:40.580 --> 00:32:44.620
Good evening!

00:32:47.700 --> 00:32:50.200
- Did you just get here? - Yes, dear.

00:32:50.290 --> 00:32:52.410
Today, I have five makeup jobs.

00:32:53.450 --> 00:32:55.290
So exhausting.

00:32:56.830 --> 00:32:59.120
Why is your face like that? Where's Sandra?

00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:01.330
She's in her room talking to her husband.

00:33:04.750 --> 00:33:07.410
So what are you doing here?

00:33:08.040 --> 00:33:09.950
I saw Dadong's figure.

00:33:10.040 --> 00:33:11.290
And it's Sandra.

00:33:11.370 --> 00:33:13.580
What do you mean? I don't understand.

00:33:13.660 --> 00:33:16.290
Your friend, Sandra, can do Leyak magic.

00:33:16.950 --> 00:33:20.200
You're mistaken, Gayatri. There's
no way she can do Leyak magic.

00:33:20.290 --> 00:33:21.726
She doesn't even come here that often.

00:33:21.750 --> 00:33:23.450
- But it's true. - Impossible.

00:33:25.040 --> 00:33:26.950
What are you talking about? Looks exciting.

00:33:27.040 --> 00:33:28.040
Why didn't you call me?

00:33:28.620 --> 00:33:32.000
Nothing. It's just Gayatri.

00:33:32.910 --> 00:33:35.750
She said she saw mystical things here.

00:33:37.040 --> 00:33:40.500
Right, like that time when I came here

00:33:40.580 --> 00:33:41.580
to my friend's villa.

00:33:41.620 --> 00:33:45.660
There is a strong mystical aura.

00:33:46.330 --> 00:33:47.750
My friends and I intentionally

00:33:47.830 --> 00:33:49.950
entered the other realm.

00:33:51.330 --> 00:33:53.540
In the end,

00:33:53.620 --> 00:33:55.080
I believe in mystical things.

00:33:55.870 --> 00:33:56.910
"Believe"?

00:33:57.540 --> 00:33:59.790
Aren't you the one who knows Leyak magic?

00:33:59.870 --> 00:34:00.870
What do you mean?

00:34:00.950 --> 00:34:04.410
From the moment you arrived, you've
been saying I practice Leyak magic.

00:34:04.500 --> 00:34:06.580
Den, tell your relative here

00:34:06.660 --> 00:34:09.290
if she's not afraid of me eating…

00:34:32.330 --> 00:34:33.790
Mr. Rai!

00:34:33.870 --> 00:34:37.040
- Sandra, wake up! - Sir!

00:34:40.700 --> 00:34:42.290
Wake up, San.

00:34:43.080 --> 00:34:44.950
San, wake up.

00:34:46.290 --> 00:34:47.700
San, wake up.

00:35:27.660 --> 00:35:30.250
- Greetings, Jero. - Greetings.

00:35:30.330 --> 00:35:31.620
Have a seat, child.

00:35:37.450 --> 00:35:40.500
You came here finally.

00:35:41.700 --> 00:35:42.700
What do you mean?

00:35:44.120 --> 00:35:45.120
Back then,

00:35:45.790 --> 00:35:48.450
your grandma came here.

00:35:51.450 --> 00:35:52.580
And now,

00:35:53.540 --> 00:35:55.080
I feel

00:35:55.870 --> 00:35:57.750
your grandma has come back again.

00:35:59.200 --> 00:36:01.540
You mean she came back from the dead?

00:36:01.620 --> 00:36:04.830
No. Not her.

00:36:05.700 --> 00:36:08.620
It's her black magic.

00:36:10.200 --> 00:36:11.200
Back then,

00:36:12.620 --> 00:36:15.660
when my grandma was
paralyzed for five years,

00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:18.370
a paranormal expert came to our house.

00:36:18.910 --> 00:36:22.120
He told us about Grandma's
knowledge of Leyak.

00:36:26.620 --> 00:36:29.200
She used to be a snake dancer.

00:36:30.700 --> 00:36:32.580
She used to perform in many villas

00:36:33.160 --> 00:36:35.200
and on stages by invitation.

00:36:36.120 --> 00:36:37.370
Many people insulted

00:36:37.450 --> 00:36:40.200
and humiliated her for
being a snake dancer,

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.040
so she tried to find a magic charm.

00:36:47.950 --> 00:36:51.370
She used Leyak magic for self-protection.

00:36:52.000 --> 00:36:54.200
So everyone would be
content and submit to her.

00:36:55.000 --> 00:36:57.950
This is what we call Penangkeb.

00:37:00.450 --> 00:37:01.450
Then

00:37:02.040 --> 00:37:04.580
you carried out the Matur Piuning ritual.

00:37:05.250 --> 00:37:07.250
Yes, Jero.

00:37:18.700 --> 00:37:20.160
But strangely,

00:37:20.250 --> 00:37:23.660
she opened her eyes and
then closed them back.

00:37:23.750 --> 00:37:27.540
It felt like something
came out of her body.

00:37:27.620 --> 00:37:28.700
That's right.

00:37:29.330 --> 00:37:31.700
Her magic came out

00:37:33.950 --> 00:37:37.040
and had to return to the amulet

00:37:37.700 --> 00:37:39.120
that she brought.

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:41.160
Amulet?

00:37:46.000 --> 00:37:47.700
What is this, Grandma?

00:37:48.950 --> 00:37:50.160
It's for my protection.

00:37:50.250 --> 00:37:51.910
Where did you get that?

00:37:52.830 --> 00:37:55.160
It was from Mangku Tedja.

00:37:55.250 --> 00:37:57.000
Who is Mangku Tedja, Grandma?

00:37:57.080 --> 00:37:59.000
You asked too many questions, girl.

00:38:00.200 --> 00:38:02.200
So where is it now?

00:38:03.160 --> 00:38:04.950
That's what we have to find out.

00:38:06.410 --> 00:38:08.290
When she died,

00:38:09.290 --> 00:38:11.200
did you find the amulet?

00:38:12.160 --> 00:38:13.160
No, Jero.

00:38:14.750 --> 00:38:16.580
We pray and hope

00:38:16.660 --> 00:38:20.080
God will show us the way.

00:38:20.950 --> 00:38:22.290
All right, Jero.

00:38:42.250 --> 00:38:43.250
Den.

00:38:44.830 --> 00:38:46.000
Wake up, Den.

00:38:47.830 --> 00:38:50.540
It's still nighttime. Just sleep.

00:38:50.620 --> 00:38:52.620
It's already afternoon, Den.

00:38:55.330 --> 00:38:56.330
Afternoon?

00:38:57.040 --> 00:38:58.040
What time is it?

00:38:59.160 --> 00:39:00.330
Oh my god.

00:39:00.950 --> 00:39:02.000
It's already 10 o'clock.

00:39:03.080 --> 00:39:04.290
You're awake, San?

00:39:05.200 --> 00:39:07.830
What happened last night?

00:39:07.910 --> 00:39:11.750
Why are you sitting on the
floor like that, watching over me?

00:39:12.370 --> 00:39:13.540
You really don't remember?

00:39:14.950 --> 00:39:16.830
You were possessed yesterday.

00:39:16.910 --> 00:39:18.120
That's why I sleep here.

00:39:18.750 --> 00:39:20.700
What? Possessed?

00:39:22.950 --> 00:39:24.950
So, where is Gayatri?

00:39:26.540 --> 00:39:28.830
Yes, San. Yesterday, you were possessed.

00:39:29.540 --> 00:39:32.040
If you don't believe it, just ask Mr. Rai.

00:39:32.120 --> 00:39:34.120
He sprinkled you with holy water.

00:39:35.080 --> 00:39:36.750
As for Gayatri,

00:39:37.500 --> 00:39:38.700
you threw her out

00:39:38.790 --> 00:39:42.040
because whoever is inside
your body doesn't like her.

00:39:42.120 --> 00:39:43.370
They're against each other.

00:39:45.040 --> 00:39:47.370
I don't even know anymore. I'm confused.

00:39:48.200 --> 00:39:49.410
That's enough.

00:39:49.500 --> 00:39:50.950
No need to get all confused.

00:39:51.040 --> 00:39:54.870
Today, we're going out. How about that?

00:39:55.790 --> 00:39:56.830
Sure.

00:39:57.500 --> 00:39:59.120
Putra also told me to go out

00:39:59.200 --> 00:40:00.870
since I'm here.

00:40:00.950 --> 00:40:04.450
Yeah, he's right. You keep
staying here in the villa.

00:40:05.290 --> 00:40:08.330
Basically, in an hour,

00:40:08.410 --> 00:40:11.200
you should be showered, dressed up,

00:40:11.290 --> 00:40:12.160
and all ready.

00:40:12.250 --> 00:40:13.870
Basically all that.

00:40:14.450 --> 00:40:16.830
Get ready in an hour from now. Get up.

00:40:17.700 --> 00:40:18.750
Don't go back to sleep.

00:40:43.870 --> 00:40:45.450
- Mom. - Yes?

00:40:45.540 --> 00:40:47.910
I want to tell you
something very important.

00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:48.870
What is it?

00:40:48.950 --> 00:40:51.370
Yesterday, I meditated.

00:40:51.450 --> 00:40:55.160
Suddenly, there was white
smoke that took me somewhere.

00:40:55.250 --> 00:40:56.620
Where's that?

00:40:56.700 --> 00:40:58.540
At the house of a spiritual person.

00:40:58.620 --> 00:41:01.330
The spiritual person knows about Grandma.

00:41:01.410 --> 00:41:02.660
What else?

00:41:02.750 --> 00:41:04.250
She said

00:41:04.330 --> 00:41:06.410
Grandma's Leyak magic has come back.

00:41:07.040 --> 00:41:09.040
It resides in her amulet.

00:41:12.540 --> 00:41:13.750
In that case,

00:41:14.700 --> 00:41:16.120
we must pray

00:41:17.040 --> 00:41:19.120
so that nothing happens.

00:41:19.200 --> 00:41:20.200
Yes, Mom.

00:41:25.790 --> 00:41:27.040
Hurry up, you baboon.

00:41:30.250 --> 00:41:31.500
You're too heavy.

00:41:31.580 --> 00:41:33.080
Wait, let's take a selfie.

00:41:36.540 --> 00:41:37.540
Playing hopscotch.

00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:40.450
It's like playing hopscotch.

00:41:49.080 --> 00:41:50.080
Den.

00:41:51.120 --> 00:41:53.750
Den, isn't this used to be a river?

00:41:53.830 --> 00:41:56.160
Yes, that's right.

00:41:56.250 --> 00:41:58.330
It's called Tukad Badung.

00:41:58.410 --> 00:42:01.830
But the millennials call it

00:42:01.910 --> 00:42:04.500
Tukad Korea!

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:10.450
This is nice. I'm happy to see
it. It's like being in Korea.

00:42:11.370 --> 00:42:12.750
I want to take some photos.

00:42:26.200 --> 00:42:27.200
Hello.

00:42:27.700 --> 00:42:28.620
Gayatri.

00:42:28.700 --> 00:42:30.160
Yeah, what's up?

00:42:30.700 --> 00:42:33.080
- Nothing. - How is Sandra doing?

00:42:33.160 --> 00:42:35.620
Sandra is fine now.

00:42:36.250 --> 00:42:40.080
She just didn't know
what happened yesterday.

00:42:40.700 --> 00:42:42.620
You have to help me, okay?

00:42:42.700 --> 00:42:45.950
Let's find out what's
really going on with Sandra.

00:42:46.040 --> 00:42:47.950
I have a spiritual teacher.

00:42:48.040 --> 00:42:49.830
I'll try to consult him.

00:42:50.450 --> 00:42:53.250
- I'll call you back. - Okay.

00:42:53.330 --> 00:42:54.700
Who's calling?

00:42:55.410 --> 00:42:57.290
So nosy. It was Mr. Bald.

00:42:57.370 --> 00:43:00.160
Mr. Bald called me. Come on.

00:43:03.540 --> 00:43:04.660
Sandra.

00:43:05.370 --> 00:43:07.540
I brought you a drink.

00:43:08.250 --> 00:43:10.410
- You're being too kind. - Of course.

00:43:14.290 --> 00:43:15.750
Cheers first, dear.

00:43:19.620 --> 00:43:22.410
How's our walk today? Was it fun?

00:43:22.500 --> 00:43:23.660
It was.

00:43:23.750 --> 00:43:25.330
I'm not even mad.

00:43:25.410 --> 00:43:26.540
That's why I swim.

00:43:26.620 --> 00:43:28.910
What are you doing there? Come and swim.

00:43:29.000 --> 00:43:30.950
Are you just leaving me here?

00:43:31.040 --> 00:43:32.370
I don't want to.

00:43:32.450 --> 00:43:34.450
- Just keep swimming.
- You want to swim or not?

00:43:34.540 --> 00:43:36.410
No way, get out.

00:43:38.870 --> 00:43:40.000
No way.

00:43:40.080 --> 00:43:43.000
- Join me! - I don't want to.

00:43:43.080 --> 00:43:46.200
I can swim on my own. It's more fun.

00:44:02.910 --> 00:44:04.160
What the hell, San?

00:44:04.250 --> 00:44:06.660
Why do I feel

00:44:07.250 --> 00:44:09.120
there's something strange in the water?

00:44:09.200 --> 00:44:12.200
You and your mystical stuff.

00:44:12.290 --> 00:44:14.120
That's all you can think about.

00:44:15.040 --> 00:44:17.910
No, I mean this is a hilly area.

00:44:18.000 --> 00:44:20.910
The water should be
cold, so why is it warm?

00:44:21.000 --> 00:44:23.370
It feels even hotter on my body.

00:44:23.450 --> 00:44:26.080
It's better for the water to be hot

00:44:26.160 --> 00:44:28.580
than for your heart to be.

00:44:29.250 --> 00:44:31.450
This way, you won't
feel cold while swimming.

00:44:32.830 --> 00:44:35.250
- I'm serious, Den. - What do you mean?

00:44:35.330 --> 00:44:37.790
I'm serious, Den.

00:44:37.870 --> 00:44:40.290
- What was that? - Den!

00:44:42.250 --> 00:44:44.370
Den!

00:44:44.450 --> 00:44:45.660
Sandra!

00:44:46.370 --> 00:44:47.870
- Mr. Rai! - What happened?

00:44:48.830 --> 00:44:49.830
Sandra!

00:44:50.700 --> 00:44:51.790
Sir!

00:44:51.870 --> 00:44:53.120
Den, help me.

00:44:55.040 --> 00:44:56.290
Sandra!

00:44:56.370 --> 00:44:57.370
San!

00:45:02.160 --> 00:45:03.200
Sir!

00:45:03.910 --> 00:45:05.410
Where is Sandra?

00:45:06.000 --> 00:45:07.750
Sandra! San!

00:45:11.370 --> 00:45:12.370
San!

00:45:14.040 --> 00:45:15.080
Sandra!

00:45:16.160 --> 00:45:17.160
San!

00:45:19.290 --> 00:45:20.290
San!

00:45:21.540 --> 00:45:23.620
San!

00:45:24.660 --> 00:45:26.540
Come up!

00:45:27.830 --> 00:45:29.660
Come up! Hurry!

00:45:44.580 --> 00:45:47.080
- Greetings. - Greetings.

00:45:47.160 --> 00:45:48.620
Have a seat, child.

00:45:51.910 --> 00:45:55.580
It looks like you're coming here

00:45:55.660 --> 00:45:57.830
with questions, child.

00:45:59.000 --> 00:46:00.000
Yes, Jero.

00:46:00.790 --> 00:46:02.290
A few days ago,

00:46:02.370 --> 00:46:04.700
I stayed at my relative's friend's villa.

00:46:05.950 --> 00:46:09.040
Actually, she came from Jakarta.

00:46:10.000 --> 00:46:13.450
Somehow, I feel like she knows Leyak magic.

00:46:15.450 --> 00:46:16.830
But I am confused.

00:46:18.000 --> 00:46:20.200
Does she really not know

00:46:20.290 --> 00:46:23.200
or is she just pretending
because she doesn't want me to know?

00:46:24.000 --> 00:46:25.000
Okay.

00:46:35.660 --> 00:46:36.830
Indeed.

00:46:37.540 --> 00:46:40.330
There is a mystical aura surrounding her.

00:46:42.040 --> 00:46:45.160
But sooner or later,

00:46:47.160 --> 00:46:49.750
you will know the answer.

00:48:39.120 --> 00:48:41.290
Den! Denny!

00:48:41.370 --> 00:48:44.080
What's wrong with you, Sandra?

00:48:44.160 --> 00:48:47.910
I'm putting on makeup.

00:48:48.000 --> 00:48:50.700
- Sandra?
- Lately, why have you always been haunted?

00:48:50.790 --> 00:48:52.250
- Denny? - Is it that old woman?

00:48:52.330 --> 00:48:53.410
I don't know, Den.

00:48:54.000 --> 00:48:55.330
I'm confused too.

00:48:55.410 --> 00:48:58.200
Why is it so frequent lately?

00:48:59.040 --> 00:49:00.910
Being haunted by an old woman.

00:49:01.000 --> 00:49:02.290
Old woman?

00:49:04.290 --> 00:49:05.540
Could it be Grandma?

00:49:06.950 --> 00:49:08.500
Yeah, that's enough, San.

00:49:08.580 --> 00:49:12.290
Later, if you see that old woman again,

00:49:12.370 --> 00:49:14.120
bring her here to meet me.

00:49:14.200 --> 00:49:17.830
I'll put on makeup on her so she'll
look like a young woman, not old woman.

00:49:18.450 --> 00:49:20.790
Come on. Let's put on
some makeup. Smile, darling.

00:49:20.870 --> 00:49:22.540
Darling, smile.

00:49:22.620 --> 00:49:24.330
We want to put this here.

00:49:24.410 --> 00:49:26.080
Come on, smile.

00:49:26.160 --> 00:49:28.700
Smile!

00:49:42.660 --> 00:49:43.660
Grandma.

00:50:59.370 --> 00:51:02.080
- Greetings, Jero. - Greetings.

00:51:02.620 --> 00:51:04.370
What's wrong, child?

00:51:05.620 --> 00:51:07.540
You seem anxious.

00:51:08.120 --> 00:51:10.120
What are you thinking about?

00:51:10.870 --> 00:51:11.950
Here's the thing, Jero.

00:51:12.040 --> 00:51:13.580
Yesterday, I meditated.

00:51:13.660 --> 00:51:16.000
Suddenly, I was in someone's house, Jero.

00:51:17.450 --> 00:51:19.410
What did you see?

00:51:19.950 --> 00:51:23.160
Two people are talking about an old woman.

00:51:23.700 --> 00:51:24.870
Their names are…

00:51:25.620 --> 00:51:27.040
Sandra and Denny, Jero.

00:51:27.790 --> 00:51:29.830
What did they experience?

00:51:30.660 --> 00:51:33.370
One of them, Sandra,

00:51:33.450 --> 00:51:35.450
was disturbed by the old woman.

00:51:35.540 --> 00:51:37.250
Was that my grandma?

00:51:38.540 --> 00:51:41.040
Calm down, child.

00:51:41.660 --> 00:51:43.660
Sooner or later,

00:51:44.200 --> 00:51:46.910
the mystery of your grandma's amulet

00:51:47.000 --> 00:51:49.000
will surely be revealed.

00:51:50.080 --> 00:51:51.830
- Okay, Jero. - Calm down.

00:51:53.040 --> 00:51:54.040
Den.

00:51:55.450 --> 00:51:58.660
Why is it that since I arrived here,

00:52:00.410 --> 00:52:03.330
I've experienced many strange things?

00:52:08.540 --> 00:52:09.660
Especially

00:52:10.370 --> 00:52:12.660
the mystical aura in this villa, Den.

00:52:12.750 --> 00:52:13.790
It's terrifying.

00:52:15.000 --> 00:52:16.000
You're right.

00:52:16.620 --> 00:52:18.160
I feel the same way

00:52:18.790 --> 00:52:21.250
since the first time I
set foot into this villa.

00:52:22.790 --> 00:52:24.500
The mystical aura is very strong.

00:52:38.120 --> 00:52:39.120
See?

00:52:39.950 --> 00:52:41.910
What I feel is true.

00:52:44.080 --> 00:52:45.160
Maybe…

00:52:48.200 --> 00:52:50.600
I can already feel the presence
of supernatural beings here.

00:52:51.870 --> 00:52:53.830
Don't say things like that.

00:52:54.450 --> 00:52:55.870
It's already nighttime, you know.

00:53:01.790 --> 00:53:06.830
Hi, guys. Sandra and I are coming.

00:53:06.910 --> 00:53:08.500
I invite Sandra to come.

00:53:09.370 --> 00:53:12.330
Wow, Sandra is getting more beautiful.

00:53:12.410 --> 00:53:14.290
You too, Auntie.

00:53:14.370 --> 00:53:15.830
Not like him.

00:53:15.910 --> 00:53:17.580
He always acts strangely.

00:53:19.450 --> 00:53:20.750
Come and eat.

00:53:20.830 --> 00:53:22.620
- Yeah. - I happened to be hungry.

00:53:23.620 --> 00:53:25.790
I'm really hungry. Sandra, go there.

00:53:26.950 --> 00:53:28.000
Hey, there.

00:53:28.080 --> 00:53:30.290
Right, where are you both going?

00:53:30.370 --> 00:53:31.970
Why are you wearing traditional clothes?

00:53:32.040 --> 00:53:35.540
We went to a wedding reception earlier.

00:53:36.330 --> 00:53:37.830
Didn't Eric come with you?

00:53:37.910 --> 00:53:41.450
No, he was at school. I picked him up.

00:53:41.540 --> 00:53:44.910
Oh right. I forgot he has school.

00:55:05.620 --> 00:55:07.870
Come here, Den. Hurry!

00:55:07.950 --> 00:55:11.080
Look under here. There are snakes!

00:55:11.160 --> 00:55:14.000
- What are you talking about?
- There are snakes, Den!

00:55:15.790 --> 00:55:16.790
Where?

00:55:17.450 --> 00:55:19.660
Lower your head.

00:55:27.200 --> 00:55:28.790
What snake?

00:55:28.870 --> 00:55:30.290
There are no snakes here.

00:55:30.370 --> 00:55:32.290
Where's the snake?

00:55:32.370 --> 00:55:33.910
You're hallucinating, aren't you?

00:55:34.700 --> 00:55:36.120
Really. Look again.

00:55:37.750 --> 00:55:39.040
Where's the snake?

00:55:41.290 --> 00:55:42.730
Where? There's nothing there, right?

00:55:44.200 --> 00:55:46.080
Nothing.

00:56:34.410 --> 00:56:35.910
San!

00:56:36.000 --> 00:56:37.410
What's wrong?

00:56:37.500 --> 00:56:39.250
Sandra! San!

00:56:39.330 --> 00:56:40.330
Calm down, San.

00:56:40.830 --> 00:56:45.040
San! Sandra!

00:56:45.120 --> 00:56:47.450
San!

00:56:47.540 --> 00:56:49.120
Mr. Rai!

00:56:49.200 --> 00:56:50.200
Honey?

00:56:51.160 --> 00:56:53.410
Wake up, honey!

00:56:54.450 --> 00:56:56.160
- Honey! - Mr. Rai!

00:56:56.250 --> 00:56:57.950
Mr. Rai, help!

00:57:02.040 --> 00:57:03.040
San.

00:57:04.950 --> 00:57:05.950
What did you give her?

00:57:06.040 --> 00:57:07.040
This is a red onion.

00:57:07.120 --> 00:57:08.660
According to Balinese beliefs,

00:57:08.750 --> 00:57:11.330
it's used to ward off
negative aura from the body.

00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:13.500
You still believe in that stuff?

00:57:13.580 --> 00:57:15.160
Stop! Believe it or not,

00:57:15.250 --> 00:57:17.330
Bali is still full of mystical aura.

00:57:20.330 --> 00:57:21.330
Honey?

00:57:23.660 --> 00:57:25.370
- You're here. - Slowly.

00:57:27.290 --> 00:57:29.200
When did you get here?

00:57:29.290 --> 00:57:31.410
I came back to surprise you.

00:57:31.500 --> 00:57:33.580
But I'm the one surprised
seeing you like this.

00:57:34.910 --> 00:57:36.540
I don't know, honey.

00:57:36.620 --> 00:57:39.290
Recently, there have been many
strange incidents at this villa.

00:57:39.370 --> 00:57:41.500
I don't get it. I'm scared.

00:57:42.870 --> 00:57:43.870
That's enough.

00:57:44.410 --> 00:57:45.790
No need to talk about it anymore.

00:57:46.450 --> 00:57:47.830
Now Putra is here.

00:57:48.750 --> 00:57:50.160
You two get some rest first.

00:57:50.250 --> 00:57:51.250
I have to go back

00:57:51.790 --> 00:57:53.870
because my mom called
and told me to come home.

00:57:54.500 --> 00:57:56.460
Thank you for looking
after Sandra all this time.

00:57:57.450 --> 00:57:58.450
Get some rest, San.

00:57:59.450 --> 00:58:01.200
- I'm going home. - Den.

00:58:01.750 --> 00:58:03.910
Whenever you have time,
keep me company here.

00:58:04.000 --> 00:58:06.660
- I'm afraid. - Of course, San. Okay?

00:58:07.540 --> 00:58:09.370
- Thank you and be careful. - Bye.

00:58:10.200 --> 00:58:11.200
Thank you, Den.

00:58:13.830 --> 00:58:16.040
Honey, are you okay?

00:59:19.500 --> 00:59:20.500
Den.

00:59:22.040 --> 00:59:23.950
- What the heck? - That…

00:59:25.540 --> 00:59:27.290
How come it's not there anymore?

00:59:27.370 --> 00:59:29.500
There's nothing there.

00:59:29.580 --> 00:59:31.910
Impossible. There was something.

00:59:32.000 --> 00:59:34.750
There's no way I'm
hallucinating at this hour.

00:59:38.620 --> 00:59:42.500
Finally, I've finished
all my work in Jakarta.

00:59:43.330 --> 00:59:44.620
Now I can have a swim.

00:59:49.750 --> 00:59:50.750
Do you want some drinks?

00:59:51.250 --> 00:59:52.250
No need.

00:59:58.790 --> 00:59:59.790
Honey.

01:00:00.330 --> 01:00:03.040
I'm still traumatized
by this swimming pool.

01:00:03.120 --> 01:00:07.000
It's just your mystic hallucination.

01:00:07.080 --> 01:00:08.200
Don't think about it.

01:00:10.000 --> 01:00:11.750
It's better if you swim with me.

01:00:11.830 --> 01:00:12.830
Let's race.

01:00:13.870 --> 01:00:16.080
- Come on. - Bring it on. Who's afraid?

01:00:16.160 --> 01:00:18.660
We start from there and end it over there.

01:00:18.750 --> 01:00:20.160
After that, let's go back there.

01:00:23.410 --> 01:00:24.410
Come on.

01:00:24.910 --> 01:00:26.330
One, two, three.

01:00:26.410 --> 01:00:27.410
You cheated.

01:02:00.790 --> 01:02:01.790
Sandra?

01:02:02.830 --> 01:02:03.830
Sandra?

01:02:05.370 --> 01:02:06.370
Sandra?

01:02:08.790 --> 01:02:10.830
What happened, honey?

01:02:11.750 --> 01:02:13.790
- What happened to you? - Honey…

01:02:14.410 --> 01:02:16.370
Earlier, I saw…

01:02:19.200 --> 01:02:21.410
That's enough. You must be tired.

01:02:22.080 --> 01:02:23.500
Let's go to our room now, okay?

01:02:28.540 --> 01:02:30.790
Come on. What's wrong with you?

01:02:39.330 --> 01:02:40.330
What else?

01:02:41.000 --> 01:02:43.700
That's what my spiritual teacher said.

01:02:43.790 --> 01:02:47.700
There is a mystical
aura inside Sandra's body.

01:02:47.790 --> 01:02:50.870
But she only said that

01:02:50.950 --> 01:02:54.040
all mysteries will be revealed.

01:02:54.660 --> 01:02:55.660
Okay then.

01:02:56.120 --> 01:02:58.290
You have to keep me informed

01:02:58.370 --> 01:03:01.290
about the information from your
spiritual teacher about Sandra.

01:03:01.370 --> 01:03:04.870
Okay, but you need to
keep an eye on Sandra.

01:03:05.660 --> 01:03:06.790
Okay, Gayatri.

01:03:06.870 --> 01:03:08.410
I've been back and forth too.

01:03:09.290 --> 01:03:10.290
All right then.

01:03:25.700 --> 01:03:27.790
Mom!

01:03:27.870 --> 01:03:29.160
There's a snake!

01:03:32.120 --> 01:03:33.120
Mom!

01:03:37.950 --> 01:03:39.160
Mom!

01:05:53.080 --> 01:05:54.080
Honey!

01:05:55.290 --> 01:05:56.540
Honey, it's me!

01:05:57.370 --> 01:05:59.750
It's me, honey! I'm your wife!

01:06:06.200 --> 01:06:07.250
Honey!

01:06:22.950 --> 01:06:23.950
Goodness.

01:06:26.250 --> 01:06:27.950
Thank God it's just a dream.

01:06:43.250 --> 01:06:45.290
My necklace. Where is it?

01:06:45.370 --> 01:06:47.660
Honey, have you seen my necklace?

01:06:47.750 --> 01:06:50.290
What necklace? I don't see any.

01:06:50.370 --> 01:06:52.580
The red necklace I usually wear.

01:06:52.660 --> 01:06:54.410
Where did you put it?

01:06:56.080 --> 01:06:57.120
Stand up.

01:06:58.120 --> 01:07:00.290
Help me look for the necklace.

01:07:00.370 --> 01:07:03.370
What's wrong with you?
It's just a necklace.

01:07:03.910 --> 01:07:06.080
The one I usually wear, honey.

01:07:06.160 --> 01:07:07.450
Why is it missing?

01:07:07.540 --> 01:07:10.370
Maybe it fell and you forgot where it is.

01:07:11.330 --> 01:07:13.950
I don't care. I just want it back.

01:09:24.080 --> 01:09:25.250
Mom has appeared

01:09:26.700 --> 01:09:28.500
in my dreams twice already.

01:09:30.750 --> 01:09:32.120
What does it mean?

01:09:34.410 --> 01:09:35.660
I have a bad feeling.

01:09:37.790 --> 01:09:40.950
As if something bad will happen.

01:09:43.660 --> 01:09:45.080
Maybe I should

01:09:46.790 --> 01:09:49.370
visit the spiritual person.

01:10:19.160 --> 01:10:20.160
Honey.

01:10:22.200 --> 01:10:23.910
What is it, honey?

01:10:24.000 --> 01:10:25.700
I want to go take a swim.

01:10:25.790 --> 01:10:26.950
Do you want to join?

01:10:27.620 --> 01:10:29.450
No, I'm already showering.

01:10:29.540 --> 01:10:30.750
You go ahead.

01:10:30.830 --> 01:10:31.950
I see.

01:10:32.040 --> 01:10:33.660
Then I'll go for a swim.

01:10:33.750 --> 01:10:35.500
Find me at the swimming pool, okay?

01:10:57.160 --> 01:10:58.500
Leyak?

01:11:00.790 --> 01:11:02.830
I heard someone say Leyak.

01:11:07.450 --> 01:11:09.200
It's just me being delusional.

01:11:32.790 --> 01:11:35.200
Why are there a lot of snakes?

01:11:37.450 --> 01:11:38.790
That means it's true then.

01:11:38.870 --> 01:11:42.200
Those people from Jakarta
learned black magic.

01:11:49.410 --> 01:11:51.870
- Greetings, Jero. - Greetings.

01:11:51.950 --> 01:11:53.410
Please have a seat.

01:11:58.750 --> 01:12:00.200
So Jero,

01:12:00.830 --> 01:12:04.620
we came here for a reason.

01:12:04.700 --> 01:12:07.790
I want to understand what my dream means.

01:12:09.080 --> 01:12:10.750
My mother-in-law

01:12:11.330 --> 01:12:14.250
who died a long time ago has appeared

01:12:14.830 --> 01:12:17.120
in my dreams twice already.

01:12:17.750 --> 01:12:20.290
What kind of dream did you have?

01:12:20.370 --> 01:12:22.370
We were

01:12:22.450 --> 01:12:24.540
in some bushes

01:12:24.620 --> 01:12:27.580
in a cemetery or something.

01:12:27.660 --> 01:12:28.660
And

01:12:29.160 --> 01:12:33.160
we had only white cloths
wrapped around our chests.

01:12:33.250 --> 01:12:36.790
I was kneeling in front of her

01:12:37.370 --> 01:12:40.660
while she danced in front of me,

01:12:40.750 --> 01:12:43.410
like a scene from Calonarang.

01:12:45.330 --> 01:12:47.500
- Let's go. - What is it?

01:12:48.120 --> 01:12:50.120
What the hell, San? This is serious.

01:12:50.200 --> 01:12:52.540
I just arrived here.

01:12:53.540 --> 01:12:55.410
While my husband is not here,

01:12:55.500 --> 01:12:57.540
accompany me to enter the other realm.

01:12:58.910 --> 01:12:59.910
What do you mean?

01:12:59.950 --> 01:13:03.410
Do you want to take me to
somewhere in nature, Sandra?

01:13:04.040 --> 01:13:07.160
I don't know. I've been so curious lately.

01:13:07.250 --> 01:13:10.120
As to why I was always haunted
by the figure of an old woman.

01:13:12.200 --> 01:13:14.830
Then are you planning to accompany her?

01:13:14.910 --> 01:13:17.500
Do you even know where she is?

01:13:17.580 --> 01:13:19.370
Hey, stop joking around.

01:13:20.870 --> 01:13:23.370
What do you want then?

01:13:23.450 --> 01:13:26.750
I had a dream about what
happened five years ago

01:13:26.830 --> 01:13:29.120
when my friends and I were knocked out…

01:13:29.750 --> 01:13:32.160
What? Knocked out?

01:13:33.500 --> 01:13:34.500
Yes.

01:13:34.910 --> 01:13:38.200
I was with them and I
entered another realm.

01:13:38.290 --> 01:13:40.790
Accompany me, please.

01:13:41.580 --> 01:13:43.120
I don't want to.

01:13:43.200 --> 01:13:46.120
I don't want to end up the
same way as your friends,

01:13:46.200 --> 01:13:48.370
knocked out by an old woman.

01:13:48.450 --> 01:13:49.450
I don't want to.

01:13:50.580 --> 01:13:53.660
I'm begging you here.

01:13:53.750 --> 01:13:56.120
Gosh, I'll shave your head, you know?

01:13:58.660 --> 01:14:00.500
Fine, I'll do it.

01:14:00.580 --> 01:14:03.370
But I don't know how to do it.

01:14:03.950 --> 01:14:05.830
Come with me. Hurry up.

01:14:05.910 --> 01:14:08.790
Hold on! My clothes!

01:14:10.040 --> 01:14:13.580
Why do I feel restless?

01:14:14.410 --> 01:14:16.000
What do you mean?

01:14:16.080 --> 01:14:19.700
I'm worried about our son, Denny.

01:14:20.540 --> 01:14:21.750
All right then.

01:14:22.330 --> 01:14:24.040
Let's pray together.

01:14:24.120 --> 01:14:26.040
Hopefully, everything is okay.

01:14:26.790 --> 01:14:27.790
Yes, dear.

01:14:34.580 --> 01:14:37.750
San, are you serious? Can't
we do this somewhere else?

01:14:38.450 --> 01:14:41.540
Stop playing around, okay?

01:14:42.450 --> 01:14:43.700
Okay.

01:14:47.450 --> 01:14:48.700
Close your eyes.

01:14:51.080 --> 01:14:52.250
Concentrate.

01:14:53.410 --> 01:14:54.870
Empty your mind.

01:14:55.950 --> 01:14:57.000
Inhale.

01:16:05.160 --> 01:16:09.160
San, I don't want that
old woman to follow me here!

01:16:09.250 --> 01:16:10.410
I have to call Gayatri.

01:16:11.410 --> 01:16:12.950
Hello, Gayatri.

01:16:13.040 --> 01:16:14.750
You have to help me and Sandra.

01:16:14.830 --> 01:16:16.580
What's happening?

01:16:17.330 --> 01:16:18.540
I can't say much,

01:16:18.620 --> 01:16:22.330
but you have to come here

01:16:22.410 --> 01:16:24.290
and bring your spiritual teacher as well.

01:16:24.370 --> 01:16:25.620
Okay.

01:16:25.700 --> 01:16:28.500
I'll bring the spiritual teacher.

01:16:28.580 --> 01:16:30.250
Okay, be careful.

01:16:30.830 --> 01:16:31.830
Let's go.

01:16:36.540 --> 01:16:38.540
- Greetings. - Greetings.

01:16:38.620 --> 01:16:40.200
What's wrong, child?

01:16:40.290 --> 01:16:42.330
It feels like something bad has happened.

01:16:42.410 --> 01:16:43.870
Yes, Jero.

01:16:43.950 --> 01:16:47.040
A figure of Leyak appeared in
the villa that I told you before.

01:16:48.950 --> 01:16:51.160
It terrorized my relative and his friend.

01:16:52.700 --> 01:16:55.830
This is all the will of Hyang Widhi Wasa.

01:16:55.910 --> 01:16:57.830
That's why all of you can meet here.

01:16:58.620 --> 01:16:59.620
What do you mean?

01:17:00.200 --> 01:17:03.200
Let's go to the villa right now.

01:17:08.410 --> 01:17:09.500
Greetings, Jero.

01:17:09.580 --> 01:17:11.660
- Greetings, Jero. - Greetings, Jero.

01:17:13.330 --> 01:17:15.950
Ma'am, aren't you the owner of the villa

01:17:16.040 --> 01:17:19.450
that my friend rented for
a holiday and photoshoot?

01:17:19.540 --> 01:17:21.540
Yes, that's right.

01:17:21.620 --> 01:17:23.370
And you…

01:17:24.080 --> 01:17:25.080
You're Sandra, right?

01:17:25.660 --> 01:17:27.040
Yes, I am.

01:17:29.790 --> 01:17:33.580
I will try to peer into what happened.

01:17:50.040 --> 01:17:51.040
It is true.

01:17:52.370 --> 01:17:55.370
This is her Leyak magic.

01:17:58.330 --> 01:18:01.370
The one that you killed at the villa.

01:18:02.450 --> 01:18:04.450
That was her amulet.

01:18:07.040 --> 01:18:09.080
- Thank you. - Take care.

01:18:09.830 --> 01:18:10.830
Be careful.

01:18:13.040 --> 01:18:14.370
Right.

01:18:17.410 --> 01:18:18.410
I…

01:18:19.660 --> 01:18:21.660
I picked up something

01:18:21.750 --> 01:18:23.540
that was wrapped in a cloth.

01:18:25.450 --> 01:18:28.950
Then I made it into a
necklace with a red string.

01:18:30.950 --> 01:18:33.790
No wonder something feels
off about the necklace.

01:18:34.620 --> 01:18:36.860
I asked once when we were
at the swimming pool about it.

01:18:37.620 --> 01:18:39.040
Where is it now?

01:18:39.660 --> 01:18:40.910
I don't know, Jero.

01:18:41.000 --> 01:18:43.290
It went missing all of a sudden.

01:18:43.370 --> 01:18:44.660
That's a lie!

01:18:45.410 --> 01:18:49.580
Someone threw away the necklace on purpose.

01:18:50.790 --> 01:18:52.370
Therefore,

01:18:52.450 --> 01:18:56.450
that's why Leyak is enraged now.

01:19:00.120 --> 01:19:01.370
Where is the amulet?

01:19:03.410 --> 01:19:04.500
Sorry, Jero.

01:19:04.580 --> 01:19:07.500
I threw it away.

01:19:08.410 --> 01:19:10.910
Because I felt that since she had it,

01:19:11.000 --> 01:19:12.080
things got very strange.

01:19:14.120 --> 01:19:15.330
But honey,

01:19:15.410 --> 01:19:17.016
I've been wearing this
necklace for five years.

01:19:17.040 --> 01:19:18.660
Nothing ever happened.

01:19:19.700 --> 01:19:21.040
It's true.

01:19:22.000 --> 01:19:25.950
When Sandra took it to Jakarta,

01:19:27.790 --> 01:19:30.290
the amulet was just an ordinary necklace.

01:19:32.330 --> 01:19:33.540
However,

01:19:34.160 --> 01:19:38.290
when Sandra returned to
Bali with the necklace,

01:19:39.410 --> 01:19:41.370
her Leyak magic

01:19:41.450 --> 01:19:43.290
emerged again.

01:19:45.080 --> 01:19:47.250
What should we do now, Jero?

01:19:48.250 --> 01:19:52.160
We must find the amulet immediately.

01:19:52.250 --> 01:19:54.000
Then we burn it.

01:19:54.620 --> 01:19:56.750
Don't wait until midnight.

01:19:57.330 --> 01:20:00.580
So that you don't get killed.

01:20:01.660 --> 01:20:03.700
Where did you throw away that necklace?

01:20:03.790 --> 01:20:05.370
In the bushes in front of the house.

01:20:06.330 --> 01:20:08.910
Hurry. Find the necklace now.

01:20:09.540 --> 01:20:11.910
I will use this incense to help us.

01:20:12.580 --> 01:20:13.660
Look for it now!

01:20:31.330 --> 01:20:32.330
Honey.

01:20:33.330 --> 01:20:35.290
Where did you throw it?

01:20:35.910 --> 01:20:37.540
It should be over here,

01:20:37.620 --> 01:20:38.790
but why is it not here?

01:20:41.290 --> 01:20:43.250
It's better if we just split up

01:20:43.330 --> 01:20:44.950
so we can find it faster.

01:20:45.040 --> 01:20:46.040
Yeah.

01:23:28.700 --> 01:23:30.200
That amulet

01:23:31.250 --> 01:23:33.200
has been found.

01:23:33.950 --> 01:23:34.950
Honey.

01:23:42.120 --> 01:23:43.120
Remember.

01:23:44.290 --> 01:23:45.870
Whoever burns it

01:23:45.950 --> 01:23:48.080
should be one of her relatives.

01:23:49.580 --> 01:23:52.410
Don't let your mind go blank.

01:23:53.290 --> 01:23:54.750
Burn the amulet.

01:23:57.120 --> 01:24:00.000
Remember, don't let your mind go blank.

01:24:30.160 --> 01:24:32.580
Lights.

01:25:40.080 --> 01:25:41.330
Hurry up!

01:25:47.950 --> 01:25:49.870
If you're scared, just go upstairs.

01:26:21.000 --> 01:26:22.750
- Stand up. - Take it with you, take it.

01:26:22.830 --> 01:26:25.870
Don't leave the headstone
here. Bring it along.

01:26:28.120 --> 01:26:30.750
Just carry this. Where's the headstone?

01:27:17.950 --> 01:27:19.370
I can finally talk.

01:27:19.450 --> 01:27:21.226
Before, the canker sore was
on top. Now it's at the bottom.

01:27:21.250 --> 01:27:23.080
No need to get angry about it.

01:27:44.950 --> 01:27:45.950
Eric?

01:27:47.410 --> 01:27:48.410
Eric.

01:27:51.330 --> 01:27:52.330
Eric?

01:27:52.870 --> 01:27:53.870
Fatso!